OL,3,CWho are the people in the asylum
OL,4,Cbacklog that the government is
OL,5,Cclearing?
OL,7,FA group that supports women who are
OL,8,Fasylum seekers in South Manchester
OL,9,Fsays life can be a "struggle" for
OL,10,Fthem, and they've never seen demand
OL,11,Flike it.
OL,13,FCaritas Shrewsbury work in and around
OL,14,FManchester, and have been working with
OL,15,Fthose in hotels for the last four and
OL,16,Fa half years.
