OL,3,CWho are the people in the asylum
OL,4,Cbacklog that the government is
OL,5,Cclearing?
OL,7,F"There's very little space for them to
OL,8,Fhave activities as families, sometimes
OL,9,Fthey've not even managed to get kids
OL,10,Finto schools for weeks on end. There's
OL,11,Fbeen a lot of work to improve that."
OL,13,FAmina is one of the attendees. She
OL,14,Ffled Syria to Turkey, but had to leave
OL,15,Fwhen things got difficult for her and
OL,16,Fher family.
OL,18,F"It's very difficult for families to
OL,19,Fstay in the room...no cooking, no
OL,20,Fnormal life for a long time,"she said.
