OL,3,CWho are the people in the asylum
OL,4,Cbacklog that the government is
OL,5,Cclearing?
OL,7,F"Children have a negative impact on
OL,8,Ftheir cognitive or mental health, some
OL,9,Fchildren cry I want to go home, we as
OL,10,Fa asylum seekers in the hotel, we
OL,11,Fdon't know what rights we have."
OL,13,FWhile Maryam, a former lawyer,
OL,14,Fstruggles with being stuck inside four
OL,15,Fwalls.
OL,17,F"We are still in hotel now, maybe
OL,18,F(it's been) 11 months," she continued.
