OL,3,CWho are the people in the asylum
OL,4,Cbacklog that the government is
OL,5,Cclearing?
OL,7,F"Me as a family, four person, we live
OL,8,Fin one room. We study in this room, we
OL,9,Feat in this room, we sleep in this
OL,10,Froom...any activity in this room.
OL,12,F"When I see my kids, (I think) this is
OL,13,Fbad life."
OL,15,FThe women attend the session weekly,
OL,16,Flearning skills such as sewing and
OL,17,Fcooking with volunteers teaching the
OL,18,Fwomen how to make things like outfits
OL,19,Fand shopping bags.
