OL,3,CWho are the people in the asylum
OL,4,Cbacklog that the government is
OL,5,Cclearing?
OL,7,FLana Osman, is the group's support
OL,8,Fworker and helps the women with
OL,9,Fanything from application forms to
OL,10,Fbooking hospital appointments.
OL,12,F"We hear different stories, we hear
OL,13,Fabout the suffering and struggle
OL,14,Fhere," said Ms Osman.
OL,16,F"They get #9 a week and live in this
OL,17,Fone room, in the hotel. Some of them
OL,18,Fare families of four or five living in
OL,19,Fone room.
