OL,3,CWho are the people in the asylum
OL,4,Cbacklog that the government is
OL,5,Cclearing?
OL,7,F"They're not allowed to have cook,
OL,8,Fthey don't have kitchens, so if they
OL,9,Fmiss a meal, they miss it."
OL,11,FThe government website says asylum
OL,12,Fseekers get #8.86 for each person in
OL,13,Ftheir household.
OL,15,FMr Gilchrist added: "Working with lots
OL,16,Fof other charities, and we've had
OL,17,Famazing support across the community,
OL,18,Fwe've been able to try and to make
OL,19,Fsure people have wellbeing support to
OL,20,Fimprove people's living situation.
