OL,3,CWho are the people in the asylum
OL,4,Cbacklog that the government is
OL,5,Cclearing?
OL,7,F"Right from the food that people are
OL,8,Feating which isn't suitable, day after
OL,9,Fday, isn't the right nutrition or
OL,10,Fright culturally through the lack of
OL,11,Fthem being able to take part in
OL,12,Fmeaningful activities."
OL,14,FCaritas Shrewsbury are now campaigning
OL,15,Ffor a change in government policy, as
OL,16,Fpart of the together with refugees
OL,17,Fcoalition - the largest call for a
OL,18,F"fair, new plan" for refugees.
