OL,3,CWho are the people in the asylum
OL,4,Cbacklog that the government is
OL,5,Cclearing?
OL,7,F"Over 500 different organisations
OL,8,Fsupporting the call for a fair new
OL,9,Fplan for refugees, so people fleeing
OL,10,Fwar and persecution can find safety,"
OL,11,Fcontinued Mr Gilchrist.
OL,13,F"We know the public support that - the
OL,14,Fgenerosity, the kindness, the sympathy
OL,15,Fof the British public.
OL,17,F"We want to make sure there is a
OL,18,Fproper strategic approach to welcome
OL,19,Fadn integrate, we can do so much
OL,20,Fbetter than the hotel accommodation."
